Package: fastblockjk
Type: Package
Title: Fast Block Jackknife for Linear Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Michel", family = "Nivard", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "michel@example.com")
Description: Fast block jackknife standard errors for linear regression.
    The implementation precomputes block-wise crossproducts and reuses them
    for leave-one-block-out estimates.
